   334	    Orchestrator->>TechDesign: Read index and note top-tier surfaces
   335	    Orchestrator->>TestPlan: Read gate and coverage expectations
   336	    Orchestrator->>Epic: Read feature scope and story context
   337	    Orchestrator->>Stories: Read all story files in order
   338	    Orchestrator->>Log: Record story order, dependencies, and key extracted state
   339	```
