   451	| Setup | locate spec pack, initialize config/log, read first references |
   452	| Preflight | validate readiness before any provider-backed work starts |
   453	| Story implementation | choose the story, run implementation, preserve continuation handles |
   454	| Story verification | launch fresh verification, interpret findings, route fixes |
   455	| Story progression | record receipts, update cumulative baselines, move to next story |
   456	| Cleanup / epic verification | materialize deferred items, review cleanup, run epic verifier and synthesizer workflows |
